        "Title": "No Pride in Your Work",
        "Location": "LOCATION_GOLDEN_GECKO",
        "PublicId": "127645643861",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/golden/mission_gecko/scene_gecko_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository e1c8c0a5-a506-45b6-9567-7b6df50b8877).Image",
        "Description": "Omar Al-Ghazali is rich, and has gotten to this point through the exploitation of workers in the more poor parts of the world. These people often don&apos;t have enough water to themselves, while Omar and his associates enjoy life up high in the sky drinking their fancy wine and living their lavish lives. Since they love their water so much, go ahead and give it to them.\r\rOh, and be prideful in your work 47, do not get caught on camera.",
